org.sureassert.uc.annotation

Annotation Type TestDouble


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Target(value=TYPE)
public @interface TestDouble
    Demarks a class as a test-double for a stated class. The source for the class specified by the replaces attribute is replaced by the source of the annotated class. Any references to the class within the source file are replaced by references to the annotated class.

    Note for source files containing more than one class definition
    This annotation MUST be specified on the top-level class within the source file. Note also that the replacement applies to the source file rather than the top-level class. Any classes defined in the class specified with replaces must also be specified in the annotated class.
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Nathan Dolan
